          "type": "text",
          "value": "It\u2019s one of the more expensive substack subscriptions at $18/month, but it is absolutely worth it. I\u2019ve seen it recommended by numerous people I respect including Jason Furman, Adam Tooze, Joe Weisenthal, and Paul Krugman. Those endorsements convinced me to subscribe and the Overshoot has provided me with a lot of detailed and novel data analysis of economic issues facing our world."
