    "title": "There\u2019s no substitute for being right all the time about everything ",
    "canonical_url": "https://www.slowboring.com/p/theres-no-substitute-for-being-right",
    "name": "Matt Hagy",
    "user_id": 3094604,
    "reaction": null,
