          "value": "Enjoyed your interview with Kathryn Paige Harden covering her research and recent book, \u201cThe Genetic Lottery\u201d. [1]  (It convinced me to read her book.) Has her work influenced your thinking about government policy for achieving better and fairer social outcomes? If so, how? "
